,"tag-parents-walidayn","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-virtue-al-fadail","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-eQ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17382,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/30\/be-fair-daughters-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":920,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Children: Enter Paradise by being just with daughters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has a daughter and he does not bury her alive, nor humiliate her, nor prefer his sons over her, he will enter Paradise due to her.\u201d Source:\u00a0Sunan Ab\u012b D\u0101w\u016bd 5146 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(fair) according to Ahmad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14921,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/11\/treat-women-well-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":920,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Women: Treat daughters, sisters well to enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is not one\u00a0of you with three daughters or three sisters, or two daughters or two sisters, fearing Allah regarding them and treating them in the best manner, but that he will enter Paradise.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/da