ory\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/13\/leniency-tolerance-business\/","url_meta":{"origin":920,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Leniency: Allah rewards gentleness in business","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Affan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty will admit a man into Paradise who was lenient in his buying and his selling, in his paying debts and his seeking repayments.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 410 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/23\/spoils-dhikr-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":920,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: The spoils of remembrance is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the spoils of gathering to remember Allah?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe spoils of the gatherings of remembrance is Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6651 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"